<h4 id="why-i-used-jekyll-and-github-for-my-blogs-">Why I used Jekyll and GitHub for my Blogs ?</h4>
<ol>
  <li>I wanted to be able to write from plain text editor rather than using OneNote or any other notebook.</li>
  <li>I wanted source control of my blogs</li>
  <li>I wanted versioning of my blogs</li>
</ol>

